Phase 2: Add "Points Calculation Rules" based on Phase 1

Changes:

Add points calculation logic to `/energy-summary`

According to the rules:
Exceeding the target → 0 points
Energy saving percentage ≥ 30% → 120 points
≥ 20% → 90 points
≥ 10% → 60 points
< 10% (and not exceeding the budget) → 30 points

Add the `points_earned` field to the returned results

